description: ------------------------------------- Creator : Matt Mayer Website: www.mattmeyer.africa Twitter: www.twitter.com/MattMeyerAfrica ------------------------------------- Many animals in nature will pair up in some way or another at some point in their lives. In this collection we celebrate the pairing up of animals of various species and circumstances and the magical forms that they take on when they come together, from the mating lions to the tussling elephant bulls, nature has a way of creating beauty in ways that requires 2 individuals to do so.
name: 2 by 2 (wildlife)
